steps.name: Given I am login on staging env by created timestamp project
When I navigate to menu "Mobile app" with submenu "Mobile Editor"
Then I should see Mobile screen display
When I select tab name Pages with index 1
When I add new screen with name JIT032CarouselPreviewCode
Then I should see the screen with name JIT032CarouselPreviewCode display in list Pages
When I select screen with name JIT032CarouselPreviewCode
When I select tab list with name "Layers"
When I open Search popup on item value "JIT032CarouselPreviewCode" with index "1"
When I add item "Carousel" without inputting in Search popup to preview mobile editor
When I open preview code with component mode
Then I should see the code content "M3201_MAIN_CAROUSEL_INIT"
When I close preview code panel
When I toggle on item value "Page" with index "1"
When I select item value "Carousel" with index "1"
When I toggle off Layout tree header
When I update field label "Width" of header "Carousel" with radio "%" and value "100"
